@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
database "MySQL Customer DB" as CustomerDB

Customer -> Gateway: POST /api/customers/cart/
Gateway -> CustomerService: POST /customers/cart/
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Validate JWT customer
CustomerService -> CustomerDB: Create or get cart
CustomerDB --> CustomerService: Cart record
CustomerService --> Gateway: Cart response
Gateway --> Customer: Cart created/ready
@enduml
